ading\" /> </w:latentstyles> </xml>< ![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]> <mce:style>< !   /* Style Definitions */  table.MsoNormalTable 	{mso-style-name:\"Table Normal\"; 	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0; 	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0; 	mso-style-noshow:yes; 	mso-style-priority:99; 	mso-style-parent:\"\"; 	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; 	mso-para-margin-top:0cm; 	mso-para-margin-right:0cm; 	mso-para-margin-bottom:10.0pt; 	mso-para-margin-left:0cm; 	line-height:115%; 	mso-pagination:widow-orphan; 	font-size:11.0pt; 	font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; 	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri; 	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; 	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri; 	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin; 	mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\"; 	mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi; 	mso-fareast-language:EN-US;} --> <!--[endif]-->\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\">TriCoreTraining  </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;MS Mincho&quot;;\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;PMingLiU&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\"></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\"> </span></strong></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</mce:style></div><!--:--><!--:de--><img class=\"alignleft\" title=\"Clemens Prerovsky\" src=\"/trainer/img/cp_sporty.png\" alt=\"Clemens Prerovsky\" width=\"209\" height=\"292\" /><img class=\"alignleft\" title=\"Klaus-M. Schremser\" src=\"/trainer/img/kms_sporty.png\" alt=\"Klaus-M. Schremser\" width=\"207\" height=\"291\" />Nachdem Clemens und ich lange nach dem richtigen Trainingsprogramm fr uns selbst gesucht haben und wir kein langfristig zufriedenstellendes Programm gefunden haben, kam es zu dem Entschlu, dass wir wir machen unser Trainingsystem selbst.\r\n\r\nViele Jahre haben wir mit verschiedenen Trainern und Online-Trainingsplanservices trainiert, aber sie alle hatten diverse Probleme und Nachteile, wenn man vom Beruf stressgeplagt ist und auch noch eine Familie und andere Interessen hat.\r\n\r\nSo haben wir uns entschieden, dass wir eine Organisation grnden, wo wir Online Coaching fr enthusiastische Athleten anbieten knnen.\r\n\r\nMit viel Motivation haben wir das Trainingsplan-Service-Projekt 2009 gestartet und mit viel Erfahrung, Wnschen, Entwicklungsknnen und natrlich Knowhow von anderen gefttert.\r\n\r\nTriCoreTrainingist ein preiswertes, interaktivesOnline-Ausdauersport-Trainingsprogramm(Laufen, Radfahren, Triathlon) fr Hobbysportler, die berufsttig sind und trotzdem optimal trainiert in ihre Wettkmpfe gehen wollen.\r\n\r\nUnser Motto lautet<strong>\"Steigere deine Geschwindigkeit und verlier Gewicht\".</strong>\r\n\r\nDie <strong>wesentlichsten Vorteile aus dem TriCoreTrainings System</strong>:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Einfachste Bedienung - cooles, userfreundliches Design</li>\r\n	<li>Trainingssystem der Profis sehr einfach einsetzen</li>\r\n	<li>Speziell fr berufsttige Sportler abgestimmt</li>\r\n	<li>Gnstig</li>\r\n	<li>Voll interaktiv - reagiert auf Vernderungen / Umgebung der Sportler</li>\r\n	<li>Spezifisches Training mit berblick ber die Trainingsphasen</li>\r\n	<li>Hchster Trainingserfolg, minimaler Invest in die Trainingsplan-Erstellung</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDas Trainingsprogramm richtet sich nach dem medizinisch anerkannten System der Periodisierung mit einer wiederholenden Belastung und Entlastung. Das System teilt deine Trainingssaison in verschiedene Phasen ein und liefert je nach Sportart optimale Trainingseinheiten fr Laufen, Radfahren und Schwimmen.\r\n\r\nEgal, ob Du einen Triathlon (Ironman, Halbironman, olympische Distanz oder Sprintdistanz), einen Laufbewerb (Marathon, Halbmarathon, 5-10 km Lauf) oder einen Radwettkampf (30-300 km) anstrebst, das TriCoreTraining Trainingsprogramm untersttzt dich in der Trainingsplan-Erstellung, in der Erfassung von Trainingseinheiten mit essentiellen Statistiken.\r\n\r\nInnerhalb krzester Zeit wirst du deine Trainingsziele erreichen und dabei auch noch Gewicht abnehmen.\r\n\r\n<strong>\"Steigere deine Geschwindigkeit und verlier Gewicht!</strong>\"\r\n\r\nWir werden das interaktive Online-Trainingsplan-Service verbessern und erweitern und hoffe, dass es es genauso groartig findest!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.getsatisfaction.com/tricoretraining\" target=\"_blank\">Gib uns doch bitte Feedback!</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.tricoretraining.com/blog/zh/tricoretraining-the-interactive-online-training-coach-for-triathlon-running-biking/\">TriCoreTraining  </a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.tricoretraining.com/blog/es/tricoretraining-the-interactive-online-training-coach-for-triathlon-running-biking/\">TriCoreTraining  el entrenador de capacitacin interactiva en lnea para el triatln, correr, andar en bicicleta</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.tricoretraining.com/blog/fr/tricoretraining-the-interactive-online-training-coach-for-triathlon-running-biking/\">TriCoreTraining  lentraneur de formation interactive en ligne pour le triathlon, course, vlo</a><!--:--><!--:zh-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nenthusiatic\r\n\r\n2009\r\n\r\nTriCoreTraining\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTriCoreTraining\r\n\r\n* - \r\n* - \r\n*/\r\n*\r\n* - \r\n*\r\n*\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n5-1030-300TriCoreTraining\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTriCoreTraining<!--:--><!--:es-->En  la actualidad, hemos traducido este artculo con Google Translate, pero  pronto vamos a tener una traduccin profesional en su idioma!\r\n\r\nClemens  y yo estbamos buscando para el programa de entrenamiento perfecto para  nosotros durante mucho tiempo pero no pudimos encontrar un entrenador  en lnea de satisfaccin para nosotros. Durante  muchos aos hemos formado con varios entrenadores y servicios en lnea  programa de entrenamiento, pero todos ellos tenan algunos o muchos  problemas e inconvenientes, si usted es un empleado ocupado con una  familia y otros intereses.\r\n\r\nAs que decidimos crear una organizacin donde podemos ofrecer un coche en lnea para los deportistas entusiastas.\r\n\r\nCon  mucha motivacin empezamos el proyecto de programa de entrenamiento en  servicio en 2009 y se alimenta el proyecto con toda nuestra experiencia,  los deseos, el desarrollo de habilidades y por supuesto el conocimiento  de los dems.\r\n\r\nTriCoreTraining  es una barata e interactiva de resistencia en lnea de formacin  deportiva (correr, ciclismo, triatln) para los atletas aficionados que  estn trabajando (tal vez tienen una familia) y quieres estar  perfectamente preparado para sus competiciones o las metas deportivas.\r\n\r\nNuestro lema: \"la velocidad de ganancia, perder peso\".\r\n\r\nLos principales beneficios para usted, si usted decide utilizar el sistema de TriCoreTraining:\r\n\r\n* Fcil manejo - diseo fresco, fcil de usar\r\n* Formacin de los profesionales del sistema - fcil de usar\r\n* Optimizado para los atletas empleados / trabajo\r\n* Baratos\r\n* Totalmente interactivo - reacciona a los cambios del atleta o el medio ambiente\r\n* la formacin especfica con informacin general sobre las fases de formacin\r\n* El mejor xito de la formacin, un mnimo de invertir en la creacin de programas de entrenamiento\r\n\r\nEl  sistema de formacin sigue el sistema conocido y aprobado mdicamente  de la periodizacin, con una carga de repeticin y de socorro. El  sistema divide la temporada en varias fases y proporciona ejercicios de  entrenamiento perfecto para correr, andar en bicicleta o nadar  (dependiendo de sus objetivos).\r\n\r\nNo  importa si quieres terminar un triatln (Ironman, medio Ironman,  distancia olmpica o la distancia sprint), la raza de los corredores  (maratn, medio maratn, correr 5-10 km) o una carrera de bicicletas (30  a 300 kilometros ),  el sistema TriCoreTraining le apoya en la creacin de programas de  entrenamiento especficos para que las estadsticas esenciales.\r\n\r\nEn poco tiempo vas a lograr sus metas y perder peso.\r\n\r\n\"Aumento de velocidad, bajar de peso\".\r\n\r\nVamos  a mejorar y potenciar este sistema de capacitacin interactiva en lnea  y esperamos que encuentre TriCoreTraining impresionante!<!--:--><!--:fr-->Actuellement,  nous avons traduit cet article avec Google translate, mais bientt nous  aurons une traduction professionnelle dans votre langue!\r\n\r\nClemens  et moi tions  la recherche du programme de formation parfait pour  nous depuis longtemps mais nous n\'avons pas pu trouver un coach en ligne  pour nous satisfaire. Pendant  de nombreuses annes, nous avons form avec les entraneurs diffrents  et des services en ligne calendrier de formation, mais ils avaient tous  une ou plusieurs des problmes et des inconvnients si vous tes un  employ occup par une famille et d\'autres intrts.\r\n\r\nNous avons donc dcid de crer une organisation o l\'on peut fournir un coach en ligne pour les athltes enthousiastes.\r\n\r\nAvec  beaucoup de motivation que nous avons commenc le projet de service  calendrier de formation en 2009 et ont aliment le projet avec toute  notre exprience, les souhaits, le dveloppement des comptences et bien  sr la connaissance des autres.\r\n\r\nTriCoreTraining  est un bon march, service interactif de formation en ligne sports  d\'endurance (marche, vlo, triathlon) pour les athltes amateurs qui  travaillent (peut-tre avoir une famille) et que vous voulez tre  parfaitement prpars pour les comptitions ou les objectifs du sport.\r\n\r\nNotre devise: \"gagner de la vitesse, perdre du poids\".\r\n\r\nLes principaux avantages pour vous, si vous dcidez d\'utiliser le systme TriCoreTraining:\r\n\r\n* Facilit de manipulation - cool, design convivial\r\n* Systme de formation des pros - facile  utiliser\r\n* Optimis pour les athltes emploi / travail\r\n* Pas cher\r\n* Entirement interactive - ragit sur les changements de l\'athlte ou de l\'environnement\r\n* Une formation spcifique avec vue d\'ensemble sur les phases de formation\r\n* Russite de la formation le plus lev, peu d\'investir dans la cration de programmes d\'entranement\r\n\r\nLe  systme de formation suit le systme bien connu et approuv par des  mdecins de la priodisation avec une charge de rpter et de secours. Le  systme divise votre saison dans les diffrentes phases et permet un  entranement parfait pour la formation en cours d\'excution, le vlo ou  la natation (en fonction de vos objectifs).\r\n\r\nPeu  importe si vous voulez terminer un triathlon (Ironman, demi-Ironman, la  distance olympique ou la distance sprint), la race des coureurs  (marathon, demi-marathon, km de course 5-10) ou une course de vlo  (30-300 km ),  le systme TriCoreTraining vous accompagne dans la cration de  programmes d\'entranement spcifiques pour vous avec des statistiques  essentielles.\r\n\r\nEn peu de temps vous permettra d\'atteindre vos objectifs et perdre du poids.\r\n\r\nGain de vitesse, perdre du poids\".\r\n\r\nNous  allons amliorer et renforcer ce systme de formation interactif en  ligne et esprons que vous trouverez TriCoreTraining gnial!<!--:--></mce:style>','<!--:en-->TriCoreTraining - the interactive online training coach for triathlon, running, biking<!--:--><!--:de-->TriCoreTraining - der interaktive Online-Trainingcoach fr Triathlon, Laufen und Radfahren<!--:--><!--:zh-->TriCoreTraining -  <!--:--><!--:es-->TriCoreTraining - el entrenador de capacitacin interactiva en lnea para el triatln, correr, andar en bicicleta <!--:--><!--:fr-->TriCoreTraining - l\'entraneur de formation interactive en ligne pour le triathlon, course, vlo <!--:-->','','publish','open','open','','tricoretraining-the-interactive-online-training-coach-for-triathlon-running-biking','','','2011-06-06 06:26:11','2011-06-06 06:26:11','',0,'http://www.tricoretraining.com/blog/',0,'page','',0),(219,2,'2011-01-06 07:22:57','2011-01-06 07:22:57','<!--:en--><div>\n<div>\n<div>\n\nClemens and I were looking for the perfect training program for us for a long time but we couldn\'t find a satisfying online coach for us. So we decided to create our own.\n\nTriCoreTraining is a cheap, interactive online-endurance-training-programme (running, biking, triathlon) for hobby athletes who are working and want to be perfectly prepared for their competitions / goals.\n\nOur motto:\"Gain speed, loose weight\".\n\nThe main benefits for your if you decide to use TriCoreTraining:\n<ul>\n	<li>Easy handling - cool, userfriendly design</li>\n	<li>Training system of the pros - easy to use</li>\n	<li>Optimized for employed / working athletes</li>\n	<li>Cheap</li>\n	<li>Fully interactive - reacts on changes of the athlete or environment</li>\n	<li>Specific training with overview about the training phases</li>\n	<li>Highest training success, minimal invest in creating training schedules</li>\n</ul>\nThe training system follows the well-known and medically approved system of periodization with a repeating load and relief. The system divides your season in various phases and provides perfect training workouts for running, biking or swimming (depending on your goals).\n\nDoesn\'t matter if you want to finish a triathlon (Ironman, half-Ironman, olympic distance or sprint distance), a runners\' race (marathon, half marathon, 5-10 km run) or a bike race (30-300 km), the TriCoreTraining system supports you in creating training schedules specific for you with essential statistics.\n\nWithin a short time you will achieve your goals and loose weight.\n\n\"Gain speed, loose weight\".\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><!--:-->','<!--:en-->TriCoreTraining - the interactive online training coach for triathlon, running, biking<!--:--><!--:de-->TriCoreTraining - der interaktive Online-Trainingcoach fr Triathlon, Laufen und Radfahren<!--:-->','','inherit','open','open','','218-revision','','','2011-01-06 07:22:57','2011-01-06 07:22:57','',218,'http://www.tricoretraining.com/blog/218-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(223,2,'2011-01-06 08:12:00','2011-01-06 08:12:00','<!--:en-->Translated by google translate (please be aware that only the German articles of club are legally valid for you!)\r\n\r\n<strong>Articles of Club</strong>\r\n\r\n 1 Name and office of the club\r\n\r\nThe club is named \"TriCoreTraining - Club for the aid of endurance sports in Austria\" and is located in A-1010 Vienna, Gonzagagasse 11/25.\r\n\r\n 2 Purpose of the Club\r\n\r\nThe club\'s activity is charitable within the meaning of the federal law (Bundesabgabenordnung) and not-for-profit.The association will meet its purpose free of political and ideological influences. We subscribe to a democratic Austria.The association aims to physical and spiritual exercises of its members, the ideal education in the field of endurance sports (triathlon, running, cycling) and the general promotion of the endurance sport in Austria and the State of Austria as a tourist destination for endurance athletes from other countries.\r\n\r\nTo achieve the Club\'s objectives are the following non-material resources:\r\n\r\na) Information, support and promotion of its members according to the principles of modern physical education and sport, especially in endurance sports (triathlon, running, swimming, cycling and similar).\r\nb) Intellectual and technical education and training in sport, by providing training and competitions for the purposes of amateur sport.\r\nc) events to recruit members and socializing\r\nd) publishing an online sports magazine for the general promotion of endurance sports\r\ne) publishing of print media about endurance sports\r\nf) provision of training on-line services to facilitate the preparations of members to an endurance sport events\r\ng) promoting the endurance sport in common endurance sport events\r\nh) organization of member trips to destinations worldwide competition, in particular, triathlon, running and cycling competitions\r\ni) operating an online store for sales of club paraphernalia (hats, t-shirts, shorts, accessories and similar) for endurance sports\r\nj) operation of a clubhouse for social gatherings of the members\r\nk) Operation of a club sports field for the promotion of endurance sports\r\n\r\n 3 ways to achieve the Association\'s aims\r\n\r\nThe necessary material resources to be raised by:\r\n\r\na) membership fees and subscriptions\r\nb) donations, grants, advertisements in the media society and other grants (sponsored by revenue)\r\nc) Income from social events (slide shows, sporting events, flea market, ...)\r\nd) Income from the sales of print media\r\ne) training company in endurance sports\r\nf) organization of joint endurance sports (triathlon events, running events, racing events in the broadest sense)\r\n\r\n 4 usage of funds of association\r\n\r\nThe Association funds may only be used in the statutes for the purposes stated.The members of the association may not receive a share of profits and in their capacity as members of any other benefits from the association.If the member leaves the club and at its dissolution, the members of the association may not receive more than the paid-up share capital and the common value of their contribution in kind.It may be favored by the association or inappropriate administrative costs incurred by disproportionately high remuneration.\r\n\r\n 5 Creation of association\r\n\r\nThe association is formed by the acceptance of members and renewed. All persons of both sexes canapply for membership.\r\n\r\n 6 Types of membership\r\n\r\nThe association\'s members are divided into ordinary, extraordinary and honorary members.\r\n\r\nFull members are those who exercise at the club, either sports or holding a function. The active and passive election is available to the ordinary members under 16 years of age, as the honorary members.\r\n\r\nAssociate members are minors under 16 and children (with reduced fee) and those that promote the association\'s activities by paying a higher membership fee.\r\n\r\nHonorary members may be appointed persons who have given meritorious service to the club and are appointed on the request of the Board of the